    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="667"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d667">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Storer</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-08-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 33 received. Following names agree with lists here: Cartegena: José R.
                    Nicolas, José de la Rosa, Enrique Dole, José Fonticoba. Ceuta: Carlos Garcia
                    Sierra, Cecilio Garcia Carmenate. Burgos: Antonio Capablanca Fernández, Julian
                    Alvarez Salazar, Norberto Rojas Hernández.</p>
                <p>You will ask their release and return to Cuba, reserving others for further
                    identification.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
